回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bf2a623dbd010525c2a3c96d46f1d9321b400ef","tid":2087003,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacd7f5e5b95df29e4e4ba0badb69438735b96a2","tid":2087003,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e94c5ddd0b61c1c0dbbf9de30133baa1a7a0bc","tid":2087003,"uid":279585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"Sogo 真特價！<br />\n<br />\n突發！Sogo 大特價，買$3000平$500！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086992\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0fe24e330ba48c0305c5634315eabb08916cc9f6","tid":2087003,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"HK Watch真係好幫到手<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日大量退出、放負po明顯有係有五毛帶頭，玩類似之前小組解散果攏野，大家唔好on99中計</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=4945dbe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱普城共諜放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4362df024478bc414fe9f117bd8ff7cbd28a6359","tid":2087003,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e748cbbfce9a40f069d3bca8e424d8d59d80e8","tid":2087003,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候到我地守護番正義女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我想破2千正評, 留個紀念得唔得"},{"pid":"390068fd8802989c5efd92bf9dd7ebb6e1993559","tid":2087003,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}